nodes.text: The Xharnoh plant was a plant that was found on Naboo. It grew on the sides of Naboo's various rivers and lakes. Their roots were used to make neural enhancers. In 1 ABY Lieutenant Karenna Dunnels of the Royal Naboo Security Forces hired a spacer to collect a number of roots to make neural boosters for the security force, prior to the raid on the Mummer bunker.
